io.confluent.ksql.serde.connect

Class ConnectFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.confluent.ksql.serde.connect.ConnectFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Format
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AvroFormat, JsonFormat, JsonSchemaFormat, ProtobufFormat

    public abstract class ConnectFormat
extends java.lang.Object
implements Format
    Base class for formats that internally leverage Connect's data model, i.e. it's Schema type.

    Subclasses need only worry about conversion between the `ParsedSchema` returned from the Schema Registry and Connect's Schema type. This class handles the conversion between Connect's Schema type and KSQL's SimpleColumn.
